# Project: Visual Direction Discovery Summary Tool

## Tech Stack
- React + Tailwind CSS
- Papa Parse for CSV parsing
- Google Gemini API (gemini-2.5-flash) for AI summarization

## Code Style
- Functional components with hooks
- Clean, readable code with comments for complex logic
- Error handling for file uploads and API calls
- Responsive design (mobile-first)

## File Structure
/components
  /VisualDirectionTool
    - index.jsx (main component)
    - FileUploader.jsx
    - SummaryDisplay.jsx
    - ExportButton.jsx
    - utils/csvParser.js
    - utils/promptBuilder.js

## Key Behaviors
- Validate CSV structure before processing
- Show loading states during AI processing
- Handle missing/optional fields gracefully
- Keep UI minimal and professional (dark theme preferred)